{"word":"H4229 - מָחָה - mâchâh - maw-khaw' - Abolish","slug":"H4229","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מָחָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mâchâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>maw-khaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Abolish"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D7;&#x05D4; - ma&#x0302;cha&#x0302;h</b> - <i>maw-khaw'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>stroke</i> or <i>rub</i>; by implication to <i>erase</i>; also to <i>smooth</i> (as if with oil), that is, <i>grease</i> or make fat; also to <i>touch</i>, that is, reach to: - abolish, blot out, destroy, full of marrow, put out, reach unto, X utterly, wipe (away, out)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4220\">H4220</a>, <a href=\"#/H4221\">H4221</a>, <a href=\"#/H4240\">H4240</a>, <a href=\"#/H4244\">H4244</a>, <a href=\"#/H4248\">H4248</a>, <a href=\"#/H4249\">H4249</a>, <a href=\"#/H4250\">H4250</a>, <a href=\"#/H4258\">H4258</a>, <a href=\"#/H4259\">H4259</a>, <a href=\"#/H4260\">H4260</a>"}]}